le":"Avengers: Endgame","video":false,"overview":"After the devastating events of Avengers: Infinity War, the universe is in ruins due to the efforts of the Mad Titan, Thanos. With the help of remaining allies, the Avengers must assemble once more in order to undo Thanos' actions and restore order to the universe once and for all, no matter what consequences may be in store.","genre_ids":[12,878,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":18.0537,"vote_count":27295,"poster_path":"/ulzhLuWrPK07P1YkdWQLZnQh1JL.jpg","release_date":"2019-04-24","vote_average":8.236,"backdrop_path":"/7RyHsO4yDXtBv1zUU3mTpHeQ0d5.jpg","original_title":"Avengers: Endgame","original_language":"en"},{"id":527774,"adult":false,"title":"Raya and the Last Dragon","video":false,"overview":"Long ago, in the fantasy world of Kumandra, humans and dragons lived together in harmony. But when an evil force threatened the land, the dragons sacrificed themselves to save humanity. Now, 500 years later, that same evil has returned and it’s up to a lone warrior, Raya, to track down the legendary last dragon to restore the fractured land and its divided people.","genre_ids":[16,10751,14,28,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.6023,"vote_count":7180,"poster_path":"/5nVhgCzxKbK47OLIKxCR1syulOn.jpg","release_date":"2021-03-03","vote_average":7.804,"backdrop_path":"/zmX7ObPaRfiCmY6LMalUb1bJDKj.jpg","original_title":"Raya and the Last Dragon","original_language":"en"},{"id":337401,"adult":false,"title":"Mulan","video":false,"overview":"When the Emperor of China issues a decree that one man per family must serve in the Imperial Chinese Army to defend the country from Huns, Hua Mulan, the eldest daughter of an honored warrior, steps in to take the place of her ailing father. She is spirited, determined and quick on her feet. Disguised as a man by the name of Hua Jun, she is tested every step of the way and must harness her innermost strength and embrace her true potential.","genre_ids":[12,14,28],"media_type":"movie",