ns shows something popping out of a closed toilet at an abandoned school.","genre_ids":[27,878],"popularity":0.249,"vote_count":14,"poster_path":"/wt1IqXEoKPtMkSAay2V9w4SJF9V.jpg","release_date":"2013-03-02","vote_average":6.857,"backdrop_path":"/bMTY4wgV9sZHBxe1cMEUEfu30P7.jpg","original_title":"戦慄怪奇ファイル コワすぎ！FILE-04真相！トイレの花子さん","original_language":"ja"},{"id":271492,"adult":false,"title":"Cut/Print","video":false,"overview":"A group of ambitious filmmakers set out to create the world's first reality horror movie. What ensues is a hellish game of cat and mouse as a cryptic filmmaker, known only as The Maestro, comes out from hiding in search of his \"perfect shot.\"","genre_ids":[53,27],"popularity":0.1648,"vote_count":7,"poster_path":"/oeYgDXOkQEURqXYPr0twVALSBxx.jpg","release_date":"2012-10-31","vote_average":5.4,"backdrop_path":"/8A8AjxiQkR4vEWpas8RddBq8h92.jpg","original_title":"Cut/Print","original_language":"en"},{"id":1842,"adult":false,"title":"The Legend of Boggy Creek","video":false,"overview":"A documentary-style drama based on true accounts of the Fouke Monster in Arkansas.","genre_ids":[12,9648,27,53],"popularity":0.3083,"vote_count":75,"poster_path":"/ewSgkgvwNboYlSZq3iHC1YkbCK1.jpg","release_date":"1972-08-01","vote_average":5.033,"backdrop_path":"/uTgXhEsfdxNMYTVDnmMzwZQsuWt.jpg","original_title":"The Legend of Boggy Creek","original_language":"en"},{"id":465155,"adult":false,"title":"Followers","video":false,"overview":"A couple who document their whole life on social media decide to go on a camping trip and share their every move with their followers. What they don't know is that someone is going to prove how easy it is to stalk someone in the digital age. Arriving at the camp site, their followers are close by and are ready to go to extreme and deadly lengths to prove their point.","genre_ids":[53],"popularity":0.434,"vote_count":25,"poster_path":"/kCcnEEZAG1bZByk1ukk4bClLcQk.jpg","release_date":"2017-07-10","vote_average":5.32,"backdrop_path":"/oVZeeRU7SQVnrI52QH3u0xBpg1M.jpg","original_title":"Followers","original_language":"en"},{"id":656211,"adult":false,"title":"Witiko","video":false,"overview":"Trying to escape from the drama-filled life she lives, young YouTube vlogger Taylor and her friends decide to go on a spur of the moment camping trip into the Northern Canadian woods. What they discover isn't the peaceful trip they hoped for, but instead a nightmarish encounter with an ancient Native American monster","genre_ids":[27,18],"popularity":0.1906,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/o3FLGWvUkLygmoPREtGyhv1srhn.jpg","release_date":"2017-07-01","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Witiko","original_language":"en"},{"id":273422,"adult":false,"title":"It Exists","video":false,"overview":"\"Ia Wujud\" follows a a group of teenagers who breaks into an abandoned theme park. Set at a time before the flurry of horror stories from the Highland Tower case, the group believes that ghosts do not exist. So they challenge each other to a 'spirit of the coin' game in the abandoned park, but they soon find that ultimately what they are looking for actually exists.","genre_ids":[27],"popularity":1.5635,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/5vAobXBwPM4zTCPlTY3fF530Ik6.jpg","release_date":"2014-05-15","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":"/rAwh6Nhsh9VkmR7djvS5BzJPft.jpg","original_title":"Ia Wujud","original_language":"en"},{"id":1457936,"adult":false,"title":"Demo_N","video":false,"overview":"An online friends' reunion has run amok when Gary opens an email containing a link to a demo of a video game, which he learns is cursed and obliviously invites a supernatural force into the chat.","genre_ids":[27],"popularity":0.193,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/4fKEDQuqGS3xs13V5Evj76Mbgdh.jpg","release_date":"2024-10-25","vote_average":8,"backdrop_path":"/cyl9kPMu1EugEAZI7LivibQveCQ.jpg","original_title":"Demo_N","original_language":"en"},{"id":468696,"adult":false,"title":"Suite 313","video":false,"overview":"Special Agent Alexander Connor is sent to investigate a house, from which a woman named Sandra has made numerous 911 calls. Things become more complicated than expected for Agent Connor, as he finds he must also rescue a police officer who responded to the home 24 hours earlier. Soon, Agent Connor will discover a horrifying secret; that Sandra is one of LUMEN CORPORATION's donors and has devoted her house to the corporation; a house which has been turned into a research lab for atrocious experiments performed on human beings.","genre_ids":[27,28],"popularity":1.1357,"vote_count":8,"poster_path":"/d7ermrJrFI9geR4XyE6IvtYTpqf.jpg","release_date":"2017-07-13","vote_average":4.6,"backdrop_path":"/abztzm2fsTkCRZhs29jCWe8Ng2.jpg","original_title":"Suite 313","original_language":"en"},{"id":1064497,"adult":false,"title":"INTERSTICE","video":false,"overview":"Two years after the tragic death of Zack Lorenzo's best friend, Andrew Ridge, Zack attends a magician show. During the spectacle, Zack becomes part of the show, and the Magician conjures a tremendous shift in Zack's perspective on the horrific incident of his past.","genre_ids":[27,53,9648],"popularity":0.2391,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/doQqQM51mezvpGF5tr6SFyoxqOr.jpg","release_date":"2022-12-16","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/6Y4GfuTONKnO2e7g90G7UTnJeDE.jpg","original_title":"INTERSTICE","original_language":"en"},{"id":659423,"adult":false,"title":"Stone Markers","video":false,"overview":"\"I see you, friends...\" So says an eerie voice in the woods that seems to haunt identical twin brothers, Cory and Connor Sherman and their three friends after they discover a strange stone marker in the woods. And when a mental patient escapes and a young boy disappears, the group embarks on a quest that uncovers information related to the disappearances of seven children more than thirty years earlier. But what starts out as an adventure soon turns terrifying as one of the boys goes missing and the remaining boys are confronted by a horrifying truth that threatens their very lives.","genre_ids":[12,53],"popularity":0.1486,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/8RoxG7C3vhlCACo0i2rYbnkwSOn.jpg","release_date":"2012-01-01","vote_average":1,"backdrop_path":"/tmJiWuEH9OncCO5Pp3mnToFbd9M.jpg","original_title":"Stone Markers","original_language":"en"},{"id":275950,"adult":false,"title":"Face: A Frat Party Massacre","video":false,"overview":"An annual Halloween fear competition between a fraternity and sorority goes awry when drugs, alcohol and the old battle of the sexes are mixed together. What is on the line? The losers must do anything the winners ask for one night. The bros won last year. They not only violated the loser but uploaded the footage on the internet. Jamie, the head of the sorority, wants vengeance. She has concocted a devilish plan to humiliate the frat brothers and come out on top. However, she is not aware that Matt, the head of the fraternity, has machinations of his own. Who will win this year? At what cost?","genre_ids":[27,53],"popularity":0.339,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/tvWLBbjtqB38pKIV55Yc875FQaU.jpg","release_date":"2013-12-18","vote_average":4.3,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Face: A Frat Party Massacre","original_language":"en"},{"id":468827,"adult":false,"title":"Therapie","video":false,"overview":"A young female felon has to do manditory therapy following her jailtime - but the therapy grows into a stalking, because the therapist is out for revenge.","genre_ids":[53,18],"popularity":0.8844,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/nbXoIQfF2nvhXgQODCW1shKuBuv.jpg","release_date":"2016-10-10","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":"/eKRVpGa60aq8P8eXXK1D9dgLJGw.jpg","original_title":"Therapie","original_language":"de"},{"id":659506,"adult":false,"title":"GHoSTbRAT","video":false,"overview":"There's a plot?","genre_ids":[27],"popularity":0.1827,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/cA4s9Uteu2h4DtwG2XVDYdqLpqr.jpg","release_date":"2019-11-20","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"GHoSTbRAT","original_language":"en"},{"id":659716,"adult":false,"title":"The Blackwell Ghost 4","video":false,"overview":"Turner returns to the light foot house to continue his investigation. This time he researched into the first victim Susan. He finds out from the detective there was a note left when light foot committed suicide. It ended up being a map to the first victim (Susan) body. The map is encrypted and turner has to find a way to decode it. While crazy things happen at the light foot house.","genre_ids":[27],"popularity":0.1404,"vote_count":35,"poster_path":"/t6rVPcRWDkJmTAlJoanrXHIn6UH.jpg","release_date":"2020-01-01","vote_average":6.4,"backdrop_path":"/zicQMV4R3kT7C1Z1IxzjeBPwDHW.jpg","original_title":"The Blackwell Ghost 4","original_language":"en"},{"id":15158,"adult":false,"title":"Phantasm II","video":false,"overview":"Mike, after his release from a psychiatric hospital, teams up with his old pal Reggie to hunt down the Tall Man, who is at it again. A mysterious, beautiful girl has also become part of Mike's dreams, and they must find her before the Tall Man does.","genre_ids":[28,27,878,53],"popularity":1.1796,"vote_count":383,"poster_path":"/cZ5mPtOXcvmg224oBM2k1db5Fnn.jpg","release_date":"1988-07-08","vote_average":6.218,"backdrop_path":"/rC2HpslTzrhzJ605DHBPkeITpt2.jpg","original_title":"Phantasm II","original_language":"en"},{"id":479965,"adult":false,"title":"Fake Blood","video":false,"overview":"Rob Grant and Mike Kovac receive a disturbing fan video inspired by their previous horror movie Mon Ami, motivating them to investigate the responsibility of filmmakers in portraying violence in movies. In their pursuit of the truth they are unwittingly introduced to the real world of violent criminals and their victims.","genre_ids":[99,27],"popularity":1.5414,"vote_count":8,"poster_path":"/ozR7YXTtng44Z7H8xNYQLhM4hab.jpg","release_date":"2017-10-06","vote_average":5.2,"backdrop_path":"/iKhxQnpFO3tGQGfMLNVN01y5hRR.jpg","original_title":"Fake Blood","o